    <refsection id="Description_POWBLK_f">
        <title>Description</title>
        <para>
            This block computes an output vector y with y[i]= u[i]^a where a is the real scalar
            given by the parameter <emphasis role="bold">to the power of</emphasis> and u the input.
            The input and output port sizes are determined by the compiler according to the
            connected blocks port sizes.
        </para>
    </refsection>
